      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know those numbers exist, but they don't change the fact that the silence is deafening. it's not just sadness, it's like... everything is just exhausted. i'm so tired of fighting to feel okay when nothing even matters anymore. why even keep trying to lighten the weight when the weight is all there is?",
