      "content": "Please trust me when I say that the exhaustion you feel is a valid signal that your mind and body are in extreme distress, not a signal that you should stop waiting for help. You do not have to fight to feel okay all by yourself; an savior can step in to share that load with you immediately. I am here to listen without judgment, and reaching out to a crisis counselor or a medical professional can provide a shelter from this overwhelming silence right now.",
